Title: iPhone Plunge Diagnostic Service
Body (HTML):
iPhone Plunge Diagnostic Service

 

At iFixYouri, we understand. Your iPhone Plunge is really important to you. When it breaks, it can really mess up your day. If you are in need of Diagnostic Service, let the professional repair technicians at iFixYouri help you out.

 

*NOTE: If you decline repairs for diagnostic or water damage treatment or your device is deemed non-repairable, you will be responsible for shipping and handling.

This is the service you need if you aren't quite sure what the problem with your iPhone Plunge is. We'll find out what is going on, and contact you with a repair quote.

 

Every repair service begins with a series of diagnostic tests to determine what the issue is. Our technicians use their repair experience to quickly diagnose the problem. In most cases, repairs are minimal; however, if we see that your iPhone Plunge has additional damage, we'll contact you before proceeding.

 

Send your iPhone Plunge to iFixYouri via the UPS shipping method of your choosing. Please ship your device in a sturdy, secure box. If you hear it rattling around in the box, add some more padding. Please do not include cases, cables, or accessories. Standard UPS Ground is covered by us, as well as $100 insurance. Faster shipping and extra insurance coverage can be purchased using the drop-down boxes above.

 

Do you have any questions about Diagnostic Service from iFixYouri? Just ask them in the box below, and we'll get back to you. Alternatively, you can always reach us via our support phone number 888-494-4349 or email support@ifixyouri.com
